♪ 你可好啊 ♪

1462
02:01:47,260 --> 02:01:50,360
♪ The greenwood is near ♪
♪ 绿林啊 近在咫尺 ♪

1463
02:01:50,480 --> 02:01:53,770
♪ And the greenwood is far ♪
